-- China Eastern Airlines Ex-Official Under Investigation, 21st Century Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-29T01:58:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/china-eastern-airlines-ex-official-under-investigation-21st-century-says.html

          
          
             A China Eastern Airlines Corp.
former general manager is under investigation for
misappropriation of company funds, the 21st Century Business
Herald reported today, citing an unidentified person.  
 Luo Zhuping, a spokesman for China Eastern, said he was
“unaware of the matter” when contacted by telephone. He
confirmed that the official, Shi Guofeng, had left the company.  
